data.text:
Name:Andy Roddick

Hometown:Omaha, NE

Birthday:August 30, 1982

About

A former World No. 1 tennis player, Andy Roddick dominates the courts.

Born in 1982 in Omaha, Neb., the award-winning player is known for his powerful serves and sense of humor-he is often overheard trading jokes with the crowd during matches.

He married Sports Illustrated model Brooklyn Decker in April 2009.
